<template>
  <navbar
    :pages="pages"
    :activePage="activePage"
    :navlinkclick="(index) => activePage = index"
  ></navbar>

  <router-view>
  </router-view>


</template>

<script>
import PageViewer from '../src/components/PageViewer.vue'
import Navbar from '../src/components/Navbar.vue'
import Calculator from '../src/components/Calculator.vue'

export default {
  components: {
    Navbar,
    PageViewer,
    Calculator
  },
  created() {
    this.getPages();

  },
  data () {
    return {
      activePage: 0,
      pages: []
    }
  },
  methods: {
    async getPages() {
      let res = await fetch('pages.json')
      let data = await res.json()

      this.pages = data;
    }
  }
}
</script>
